# 🌸 AI-Diwan — Arabic Love Poem Generator

AI-Diwan creates personalized Arabic love poems using free **ChatAnywhere GPT-4o-mini** and runs fully server-side on **Cloudflare Workers**.

---

## 🚀 Features
- AI-generated Arabic poetry in Nizar Qabbani style  
- Four modes: `classic`, `calm`, `pledge`, `velvet`  
- Mobile-friendly and lightweight  
- No API key exposure  
- Fast Cloudflare deployment  

---

## 🧠 Prerequisites
- Node.js + npm  
- [Cloudflare account](https://dash.cloudflare.com)  
- [ChatAnywhere API key](https://api.chatanywhere.tech/v1/oauth/free/render)

---

